QuestData.Title: Searching High and Low
QuestData.Description:
Three locks upon the door, three keys hidden atop the zenith.
Find the phrases. Speak the words. Secure the vessel.
QuestData.LogDescription: Gather the Ingress Phrases on the Ultimus Locus that are needed to claim the Vessel.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Pocopoc beside the Empty Vessel.
